JUST IN: Joe Biden said in his ABC interview tonight of President Trump's coronavirus response:  "I don't blame him for the COVID crisis. I blame him for walking away and not dealing with the solutions"

name: axios
text:

text:
Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern announced today New Zealand's coronavirus restrictions will remain in place until at least next week, when wearing face masks will become mandatory on public transport
